Microsoft

Core Search & AI

I'm a software engineer on the Core Search & AI Metrics team, which is constantly implementing state-of-the-art ML models to manufacture and monitor the high-quality metrics that power Bing (the second most-used search engine in the world).

Some models I've worked with include BERT, Latent Dirichlet allocation (LDA), and logistic regression for binary and multilabel classification. I'm familiar with many data science tools including Azure Machine Learning, PyTorch, visualization libraries (scikitlearn, matplotlib). I am growing my data science intuition day-by-day.
